{"h1f497df1g3452g4114ga172g335c2e68c4ac": ["A word, if you please.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "4e75039c-1412-bb5b-1585-186e4b2a2751"], "h0245c746g92a6g4cc1g8128g0551196ae3e4": ["Remember how I told you I was in dire need of magical artefacts to absorb?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "567118f9-bedb-65db-a3de-aa3b811e1a48"], "h804d189egea1cg4e5agba52gc851622df928": ["Clearly the matter has hardly been a priority of yours, but even so, you can consider it closed.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "87642b06-15da-00c0-ce84-2e56ff0e6f63"], "hadc349bbg8d73g4e47g89eageec375378fd4": ["I no longer require assistance - neither yours, nor that of artefacts.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "d7cdd6f1-9b98-3284-aed3-49fac6a13734"], "h260f43f5g40c8g45cfga273gba5eacf35f5b": ["I don't follow. This seems awfully sudden.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "7fb1f1e6-9e31-4988-6314-fa54f91e8124"], "hac62e4acgbf4ag4818gb5a5g5ae1f80c2954": ["Not at all.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "512cfadb-72b0-9ba8-fb60-282af51747b4"], "h7739abcdg0ca9g4586gb2a3g7b4946a74614": ["I've had a solution in mind for a while now, it just took me some time to... set it in motion.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "16e5916d-474a-f6d7-6c6a-370e0124869f"], "h0362ca5ag99deg4505gbf95g035fa86a18aa": ["That's it - I won't take more of your time this lovely evening. Rest well.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "29c9d2f9-fbd5-586e-2b51-6a392674419f"], "hf913df8dg5679g4bc3g8f1bg2a640053f2c4": ["<i>Something's off. Try to connect with Gale without him noticing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "d48b285f-4e4d-7a44-176c-9d6147934a27"], "h18f42b8eg27acg4b8dg8e6cgaa653a5a3f70": ["*You flutter through his mind like a bat through the night and you see...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "faa6c93b-0737-29c0-deea-dd4f540fc8d5"], "hb1b80d85g47beg487bg968dg5ea41e6fdd22": ["*... fire. You hear laughter. You smell brimstone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "12262cba-a187-613a-44fd-6d3078e6c3e5"], "h42b92ae3g7529g4385g8c77g6dbb1c471215": ["*It's the scent of Avernus.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "10b68e4c-1e37-2710-ebef-dfa3d729d3c7"], "hd0ed165cgb7c2g45c0gab36g289be37f60bb": ["Stop that! How dare you...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "28e75ad4-e949-2d01-1e04-ad7b85557ee9"], "h58983c4bgdcd1g4b5aga93bgb14fce8d1a75": ["Forget whatever it was you saw. It's all beyond you now anyway.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "64d16816-0cd8-5696-0f8c-8773aab7f4bb"], "h01df7177g466bg4da7g8f17gcd42f68346f7": ["Gale, what did you do?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "cac593f6-5567-3ac8-e320-fa22b72649a7"], "hec2dd9bcg4528g4992gab20gcc93dd425a1f": ["No more than what I had to - and that's all I'll say on the matter.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "71de4266-5f3c-4cea-b9c9-f5ef8262f6a1"], "h551d5a55g18b3g4bf4ga46cg076720198d18": ["We'll let all this rest for now, but it will be addressed again later.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "74c3ea7d-4602-26e8-6078-dec0f49378df"], "h357fb19bg6cb8g4a88gaf4eg850069d7cf6e": ["Much later. If ever.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "7ebb8b70-7df1-01f4-2b45-410fec2d6c16"], "h1537f19ag075ag499agab16g005aa8679d40": ["I don't think I want you around any longer.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "94876eea-420c-8c84-8b84-e4a4b79c7216"], "hbf660bbeg090fg4accg89b9g1ae133309121": ["Suit yourself. Like I said: I no longer require your assistance.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "8ff7cf4d-6ab0-98dc-1e17-f42c520b48ce"], "h23f0b149g0c1eg417fg982agec7151e45b92": ["Farewell.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "bee4eb20-9ef5-f75d-eaa3-9950d4c5212a"], "h765fa86cg73fbg4136gb932ga005ccdf9508": ["Stop that! How dare you - again...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "5973f635-4e52-cfb9-3d48-fbfe2f3843af"], "h239692f4g83e7g4aadg84fag3ab94bd5ffaf": ["*Mocking words drift back to you. 'This is the House of Hope.'*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "a7ad2c9c-f9a6-582f-b5e3-24f626773ffb"], "hbc7979e8gb089g4c3cga74fgd105054ad08f": ["*... nothing but darkness.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "d43fcdd0-7491-c5a7-24b1-93f806434fce"], "hb00015c7g66bdg43eeg9d00g77d09a89a608": ["Up to tricks, are we?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "2bf1d14e-03ee-8f3f-07dc-2c6c68ec2312"], "ha8a7bb90g141eg47d5g97b3g28ae8f9ee7af": ["No matter. All you see is what I want you to see.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "a073576a-138b-563f-4a38-8e8e5437f704"], "hb1037428g7118g45dagaa11g3d4dc3363e10": ["In my mind, you are quite blind.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "8be56d95-35e4-ab18-fd86-442ce2a62a7e"], "h5792275fg28b7g4bf4gb8a7g79459028b98b": ["Up to old tricks again, are we?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "af03013d-dcec-5470-93cf-05910bec0c25"], "h14f370ddg8ecag4f7fg854fg8de0ac5125b3": ["You too, Gale.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "97d97852-cca5-1287-6c8b-20af9a244fde"], "h0a650e14g4467g4ff6gae52ge147aef9cf69": ["Care to tell me why?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "e275d204-001d-5550-e6e0-717a19bedfc6"], "h1d36d224gbf8eg4657gb665g9cea0eca0338": ["Not really, no.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "7c67181a-da83-ff2e-59b6-d30659d70744"], "hc9e72aefgb268g4a71g9d5eg235f15fc4c03": ["Good to know - and goodnight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "875f5ad1-a891-d734-f4f1-563053fd7c08"], "hd7e1ab04g9384g4922gaabeg7a354e8c4f8d": ["Goodnight.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Betrayal_CRD_Gale.html", "c26d4b6c-0bbf-c1b7-8fb8-2f22fea4ffe6"]}